url: "https://mmda.ipt.kpi.ua/"
abstract: >-
  A cognitive digital twin framework for land cover change detection
  and vegetation analysis using satellite imagery, machine learning,
  and LLM-powered orchestration. Developed at the Department of
  Mathematical Modelling and Data Analysis, Igor Sikorsky Kyiv
  Polytechnic Institute.
